Class PartialMove

java.lang.Object
  PartialMove
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<PartialMove>
public class PartialMove
extends Object
implements Comparable<PartialMove>

Immutable! (Only has constructor and private fields and getters.) Holds a "single" part of a move. (one blot moves from point or bar to point or bear off) HEY: this class has a copy constructor, so if you add new fields You MUST add them to the copy constructor!

Version:
(2012 Feb 11)
Author:
(Mike Roam)
